videos.description: Wenyen Gabriel has some space and knocks down the triple for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: UK's Gabriel knocks down the 3-pointer

videos.description: Wenyen Gabriel hits his third 3-pointer of the first half after creating some space.
videos.headline: Gabriel buries third triple

videos.description: Admiral Schofield cuts the UK lead to three after knocking down a 3-pointer from the corner.
videos.headline: UT's Schofield buries a triple from the corner

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield leaks out after a steal and finishes with authority.
videos.headline: Schofield throws it down

videos.description: Kyle Alexander cuts to the basket off of the inbounds play and finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Alexander gets a big dunk off the inbounds

videos.description: Kentucky's Wenyen Gabriel takes one big dribble and takes contact while getting the layup to go.
videos.headline: Gabriel gets tough and-1 to go

videos.description: Lamonte Turner knocks down a corner 3-pointer for Tennessee to tie the game.
videos.headline: Turner ties it up with clutch 3-pointer

videos.description: Grant Williams puts up his hand and gets the alley-oop layup for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Williams finds a hole in the defense and gets the alley-oop

videos.description: Admiral Schofield gets fouled but manages to get the tip-in shot to go for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Schofield comes up huge with the tip-in

videos.description: Admiral Schofield finishes with a huge slam as Tennessee defeats Kentucky.
videos.headline: Schofield puts the exclamation point on UK
